translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  10,62,Yaad rakho kay Allah kay doston per na koi andesha hai aur na woh ghumgeen hotay hain
  10,63,Yeh woh log hain jo eman laye aur (buraiyon say) perhez rakhtay hain
  10,64,Inn kay liye dunyawi zindagi mein bhi aur aakhirat mein bhi khushkhabri hai Allah Taalaa ki baaton mein kuch farq hua nahi kerta. Yeh bari kaamyabi hai
  10,65,Aur aap ko inn ki baaten ghum mein na daalen. Tamam tar ghalba Allah hi kay liye hai woh sunta janta hai
  10,66,Yaad rakho kay jitney kuch aasman mein hain aur jitney zamin mein hain yeh sab Allah hi kay hain aur jo log Allah ko chor ker doosray shurka ki ibadat ker rahey hain kiss cheez ki ittabaa ker rahey hain aur mehaz atkalen laga rahey hain
  10,67,Woh aisa hi hai jiss ney tumharay liye raat banaee takay tum iss mein aaram kero aur din bhi iss tor per banaya kay dekhney bhalney ka zariya hai tehqeeq iss mein dalaeel hain unn logon kay liye jo suntay hain
  10,68,Woh kehtay hain kay Allah aulad rakhta hai. Subhan Allah ! Who to kissi ka mohtaj nahi ussi ki milkiyat hai jo kuch aasmano mein hai aur jo kuch zamin mein hai. Tumharay pass iss per koi daleel nahi. Kiya Allah kay zimmay aisi baat lagatay ho jiss ka tum ilm nahi rakhtay
  10,69,Aap keh dijiye kay jo log Allah per jhoot iftra kertay hain woh kaamyab na hongay
  10,70,Yeh duniya mein thora sa aish hai phir humaray pass inn ko aana hai phir hum inn ko inn kay kufur kay badlay sakht azab chakhayen gay